# File-sync (iCloud / Dropbox / OneDrive) conflict copies — "name 2.ext",
# "name copy.ext". These carry duplicate content ids and pollute the repo.
* [0-9].py
* [0-9].md
* [0-9].json
* [0-9].txt
* copy.py
* copy.md
* copy.json
